    <item>
      <title>Sony 全新 INZONE H9 II, E9  全新旗舰无线耳机、键盘滑鼠新登场</title>
      <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/08/22/sony-inzone-h9-ii-gaming-gear-expansion/parts/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=sony-inzone-h9-ii-gaming-gear-expansion</link>
      <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/08/22/sony-inzone-h9-ii-gaming-gear-expansion/parts/#respond</comments>
      <dc:creator>蓝骨</dc:creator>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Aug 2025 10:17:18 +0000</pubDate>
      <category>配件</category>
      <category>INZONE</category>
      <category>INZONE E9</category>
      <category>INZONE H9 II</category>
      <category>SONY</category>
      <category>无线耳机</category>
      <category>电竞配件</category>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1323009</guid>
      
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Sony 宣布大幅扩充 INZONE 游戏配件产品线，新增 INZONE H9 II 旗舰无线耳机及全新入耳式 INZONE E9 耳机，同时首度推出游戏键盘、滑鼠及滑鼠垫产品。所有新产品均与顶尖电竞团队 Fnatic 共同开发，专为第一人称射击游戏而设，其中 INZONE E9 更获 Apex Legends Global Series Year 5 Championship 比赛批准使用。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1323055" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_01788-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_01788-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_01788-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1323060" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_01922-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="387" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_01922-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_01922-scaled.jpg 600w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 387px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span id="more-1323009"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1323018" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/white_mk_another_her-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/white_mk_another_her-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/white_mk_another_her.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/white_mk_another_her-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;INZONE H9 II 作为系列旗舰产品，采用与 Sony 广受好评 WH-1000XM6 无线降噪耳机相同驱动单元，确保全音域音效精准清晰。耳机重量仅 260 克，配备全新设计头带均匀分布重量，确保长时间游戏保持佩戴舒适。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1323052" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_01940-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="387" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_01940-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_01940-scaled.jpg 600w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 387px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1323053" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_02005-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="387" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_02005-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_02005-scaled.jpg 600w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 387px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;耳机配备高指向心形波束悬吊式麦克风，结合 AI 优化精确度有效过滤四周噪音，让队友更清晰听到玩家声音。凭借宽阔频率范围，带来比以往更清晰自然声音表现。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1323057" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_01926-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="387" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_01926-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_01926-scaled.jpg 600w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 387px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;连接方面，随附 USB-C 转接器采用专用超低延迟 2.4GHz 连线，同时支援 LE Audio 和蓝牙配对保持同步连接，让玩家享受低延迟游戏同时保持与智能手机连接。每次充电后电池续航力长达 30 小时。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1323019" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/white_mk_front_side_-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/white_mk_front_side_-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/white_mk_front_side_.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/white_mk_front_side_-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;除了旗舰 INZONE H9 II，亦推出 INZONE E9 有线入耳式耳机，音效调校基于 Fnatic 团队反馈，确保玩家能更早察觉脚步声、子弹声及远处威胁。耳机设计纤巧确保佩戴舒适，有效降低耳部压力，提供多种尺寸隔音海绵耳塞或矽胶耳塞适应不同环境。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1323051" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_02089-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="387" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_02089-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_02089-scaled.jpg 600w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 387px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;INZONE E9 具备 Sony 首款全封闭式耳机结构，密封机身搭配隔音耳塞带来卓越被动降噪效果，无论身处专业赛事观众喧闹声中或日常游戏背景干扰都能完美应对。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1323058" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_02077-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_02077-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_02077-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;INZONE KBD-H75 则是 Sony 首款游戏键盘，备有快速触发模式，用户不需将按键重置即可快速切换输入，支援高达 8,000Hz 轮询率实现闪电般讯号传递。键盘采用橡胶垫支架吸收冲击力并降低振动，带来更柔和按压感和更清晰声效。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1323056" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_01768-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_01768-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_01768-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1323020" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/fy25_inzone_keyboard-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/fy25_inzone_keyboard-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/fy25_inzone_keyboard.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;键盘汲取 Fnatic 专业反馈，采用 75% 布局消除按键间格空隙，实现更紧凑宽度。节省空间旋钮支援自订功能如音量控制，释放空间让用户快速利落控制滑鼠。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1323021" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/fy25_inzone_mouse_mk-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/fy25_inzone_mouse_mk-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/fy25_inzone_mouse_mk.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1323059" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_02082-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_02082-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_02082-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;电竞滑鼠方面，Sony 指 INZONE Mouse-A 在灵活性和稳定性间达到完美平衡，重量仅 48.4 克。强化外壳及空心玻璃珠设计实现减重同时在压力下保持稳定性，电池续航力达 90 小时。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;滑鼠搭载 INZONE 特有高效能感应器，高达 30K DPI，加速高达 70G，最高速度可达 750 IPS。轮询率高达 8,000Hz 带来更顺畅追踪和近乎零延迟体验。光学开关利用光线传输讯号无需物理接触，大幅提升反应速度。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1323022" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/inzonematd_anglemid-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/inzonematd_anglemid-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/inzonematd_anglemid.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sony 今次亦同时推出两款专业滑鼠垫，其中 INZONE Mat-F 采用 SlimFlex 材质，厚度仅 6 毫米，阻力适中支援更精确瞄准和更畅顺制动，适合滑鼠设定较低灵敏度玩家。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;而 INZONE Mat-D 厚度仅 4 毫米，专为大逃杀游戏提供流畅滑动和高速反应而设计，低摩擦力支援快速滑动，适合需要即时反应高灵敏度玩家。两款滑鼠垫边缘扁平和防磨边缝合使缝合线位于垫底部，游戏过程中不会阻碍用家操作，更加耐用。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;售价方面，可以参考以下资料：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1323023" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/screenshot20250822at-694x172.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="172" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/screenshot20250822at-694x172.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/screenshot20250822at.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

